query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci rt t) NoMergeJoin(ci rt t mc) NoHashJoin(ci mc rt t cn) NoHashJoin(ci cn mc rt t n) NoHashJoin(ci cn mc n rt t chn) NoMergeJoin(chn ci cn mc n rt t an) */ select min(an.name) AS alternative_name,
min(chn.name) AS voiced_character_name,
min(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
min(t.title) AS american_movie
from role_type AS rt
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.role_id = rt.id AND rt.role = 'actress' AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(voice)',
'(executive producer)',
'(writer)')
inner join title AS t
on ci.movie_id = t.id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name like '%Jo%'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id
inner join aka_name AS an
on an.person_id = ci.person_id AND an.person_id = n.id;
